title: Marche Tau
description: Part of chain of several health food stores in Quebec. This location opened in 2005. Has a kitchen making takeaway food and dessert. Offers a variety of certified organic fruits and vegetable; natural and organic groceries; gluten-free products; babies products; natural cosmetics and skin care; eco-friendly household products; nutritional supplements and vitamins; herbal medicine, homeopathy, and aromatherapy.
